首先需要在项目中引入MyBatis-Plus和MyBatis-Plus的Mapper自动填充插件，然后在启动类中添加以下配置：

```
@Configuration
@MapperScan(basePackages = {"com.example.demo.dao"}, markerInterface = MyMapper.class)
public class MybatisPlusConfig {
    @Bean
    public PaginationInterceptor paginationInterceptor() {
        return new PaginationInterceptor();
    }

    @Bean
    public MetaObjectHandler metaObjectHandler() {
        return new MyMetaObjectHandler();
    }

    @Bean
    public GlobalConfig globalConfig() {
        GlobalConfig globalConfig = new GlobalConfig();
        globalConfig.setMetaObjectHandler(metaObjectHandler());
        return globalConfig;
    }

    public class MyMetaObjectHandler implements MetaObjectHandler {
        @Override
        public void insertFill(MetaObject metaObject) {
            // 自动填充create_time、update_time属性为当前时间戳
            this.setFieldValByName("createTime", System.currentTimeMillis(), metaObject);
            this.setFieldValByName("updateTime", System.currentTimeMillis(), metaObject);
        }

        @Override
        public void updateFill(MetaObject metaObject) {
            // 自动填充update_time属性为当前时间戳
            this.setFieldValByName("updateTime", System.currentTimeMillis(), metaObject);
        }
    }
}
```

这里我们定义了两个Bean：

- PaginationInterceptor：分页插件，用于支持分页
- MyMetaObjectHandler：自定义元对象处理器，用于自动填充实体类中的createTime和updateTime属性

接下来我们创建一个实体类并添加自动填充注解：

```
@Data
@TableName("user")
public class UserDO {
    @TableId(type = IdType.AUTO)
    private Long id;
    private String name;
    private Integer age;
    @TableField(fill = FieldFill.INSERT)
    private Long createTime;
    @TableField(fill = FieldFill.INSERT_UPDATE)
    private Long updateTime;
}
```

这里我们使用MyBatis-Plus的注解@TableId和@TableName，其中@TableId注解指定了实体的主键字段，并使用了自增长策略；@TableName注解指定了实体对应的数据库表名。

同时，在createTime和updateTime属性上使用了@TableField注解，并指定了自动填充操作。使用FieldFill.INSERT表示该属性在新增数据时进行自动填充，在更新数据时不进行填充；使用FieldFill.INSERT_UPDATE表示该属性在新增和更新数据时都进行自动填充。

最后，我们可以创建一个Mapper接口并使用MyBatis-Plus提供的基础接口来继承：

```
public interface UserMapper extends MyMapper<UserDO> {
}
```

这里我们继承了MyMapper接口，实现了基本的增删改查操作。然后我们就可以在业务代码中使用UserMapper来进行数据库操作了。

附：MyBatis-Plus的Mapper自动填充插件的配置方式

在pom.xml文件中引入MyBatis-Plus的Mapper自动填充插件：

```
<dependency>
    <groupId>com.baomidou</groupId>
    <artifactId>mybatis-plus-extension</artifactId>
    <version>3.3.2</version>
</dependency>
```

然后在启动类中添加以下配置：

```
@Configuration
public class MybatisPlusConfig {
    @Bean
    public MybatisPlusInterceptor mybatisPlusInterceptor() {
        MybatisPlusInterceptor interceptor = new MybatisPlusInterceptor();
        // 添加自动填充插件
        interceptor.addInnerInterceptor(new MybatisPlusFillInterceptor());
        return interceptor;
    }
}
```

这里我们将MybatisPlusFillInterceptor作为MybatisPlusInterceptor的内部拦截器添加进去。

To create your WordPress plugin for the described feature, follow these steps to get started:

1. Plugin structure:
Create a folder with a descriptive name, e.g. "scrolling-header". Inside the folder, create a PHP file with the same name, "scrolling-header.php".

2. Plugin header:
At the beginning of the PHP file, include a header with the plugin's information, for instance:

```php
<?php
/*
Plugin Name: Scrolling Header
Plugin URI: https://www.example.com/scrolling-header
Description: Adds the ability to dynamically hide and show the header on scroll.
Version: 1.0
Author: Your Name
Author URI: https://www.example.com
License: GPLv2 or later
Text Domain: scrolling-header
*/
```

3. Enqueue scripts:
Enqueue the necessary JavaScript and CSS files for your plugin. Create a function that hooks into "wp_enqueue_scripts":

```php
function scrolling_header_enqueue_scripts() {
  wp_enqueue_script('scrolling-header-script', plugin_dir_url(__FILE__) . 'scrolling-header.js', array('jquery'), '1.0.0', true);
  wp_enqueue_style('scrolling-header-style', plugin_dir_url(__FILE__) . 'scrolling-header.css');
}
add_action('wp_enqueue_scripts', 'scrolling_header_enqueue_scripts');
```

4. JavaScript implementation:
Create "scrolling-header.js" in your plugin folder. Add the JavaScript code to show and hide the header on scroll:

```js
jQuery(function ($) {
  var header = $('header');
  var previousScroll = 0;

  $(window).scroll(function () {
    var currentScroll = $(this).scrollTop();

    if (currentScroll > previousScroll) {
      header.slideUp();
    } else {
      header.slideDown();
    }

    previousScroll = currentScroll;
  });
});
```

5. CSS implementation:
Create "scrolling-header.css" in your plugin folder. Add the necessary CSS styles for a smooth animation:

```css
header {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  width: 100%;
  z-index: 1000;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
```

6. Activate the plugin:
Upload the "scrolling-header" folder to your WordPress "/wp-content/plugins/" directory. Then, log in to your WordPress admin area and go to "Plugins" -> "Installed Plugins". Locate the "Scrolling Header" plugin and click "Activate".

With these steps, you've created a simple WordPress plugin that adds a smooth scrolling effect to hide and show the site's header. Note that this may need customization based on your theme's header structure and CSS.

Here is the modified `ArrayDeck` class based on the provided template:

``` java
import java.util.Iterator;

public class ArrayDeck implements Deck, Iterable<Card> {

    private final int MAX_SUIT = 4;
    private final char[] SUITS = { 'C', 'D', 'H', 'S' };
    private final int MAX_RANK = 13;
    private Card[] cards;

    protected ArrayDeck() {
    }

    public ArrayDeck(int maxRank) {
        if (maxRank < 1 || maxRank > 13) {
            throw new IllegalArgumentException("maxRank must be between 1 and 13");
        }

        cards = new Card[MAX_SUIT * maxRank];
        for (int i = 0; i < maxRank; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < MAX_SUIT; j++) {
                cards[i * MAX_SUIT + j] = new Card(i + 1, String.valueOf(SUITS[j]));
            }
        }
    }

    public Card peekTop() {
        return cards[0];
    }

    public ArrayDeck copy() {
        ArrayDeck newDeck = new ArrayDeck();
        newDeck.cards = this.cards.clone();
        return newDeck;
    }

    public int size() {
        return cards.length;
    }

    private void shuffle(boolean out) {
        Card[] shuffled = new Card[cards.length];

        int half = cards.length / 2;
        for (int i = 0; i < half; i++) {
            shuffled[i * 2 + (!out ? 0 : 1)] = cards[i];
            shuffled[i * 2 + (!out ? 1 : 0)] = cards[i + half];
        }

        this.cards = shuffled;
    }

    public void outShuffle() {
        shuffle(true);
    }

    public void inShuffle() {
        shuffle(false);
    }

    public String toString() {
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        for (int i = 0; i < cards.length; i++) {
            sb.append(cards[i]);
            if (i < cards.length - 1) {
                sb.append(" ");
            }
        }
        return sb.toString();
    }

    public Iterator<Card> iterator() {
        return new Iterator<Card>() {
            private int currentIndex = 0;

            @Override
            public boolean hasNext() {
                return currentIndex < cards.length;
            }

            @Override
            public Card next() {
                return cards[currentIndex++];
            }
        };
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        ArrayDeck deck = new ArrayDeck(3);
        System.out.println("Initial deck:\n" + deck);

        deck.outShuffle();
        System.out.println("After outShuffle:\n" + deck);

        deck.inShuffle();
        System.out.println("After inShuffle:\n" + deck);
    }
}
```

This updated `ArrayDeck` class is based on the provided template and includes the required methods as specified in the assignment. The `main` method demonstrates how to create an `ArrayDeck`, print it, and perform an out-shuffle and in-shuffle.

非常抱歉，看来我回答的不是很清晰。如果您想在 Windows 窗体中嵌入 WebView 控件，您需要将 WebView 控件添加到一个 `System.Windows.Forms.Control` 对象中，如 `System.Windows.Forms.Panel`。

以下是示例代码，演示如何在 Windows 窗体中嵌入 WebView 控件：

```csharp
using EO.WebEngine;
using EO.WebView;
using System;
using System.Windows.Forms;

namespace MyApplication
{
    public class MainForm : Form
    {
        private Engine _engine;
        private WebView _view;

        public MainForm()
        {
            // 创建一个新的 EO.WebEngine.Engine 实例
            _engine = new Engine();

            // 创建一个新的 EO.WebView.WebView 实例
            _view = new WebView(_engine);

            // 创建一个新的 System.Windows.Forms.Panel 控件
            var panel = new Panel();

            // 将 Panel 控件添加到窗体中
            Controls.Add(panel);

            // 将 WebView 控件添加到 Panel 控件中
            panel.Controls.Add(_view);

            // 设置 Panel 控件的大小和位置
            panel.Dock = DockStyle.Fill;

            // 导航到页面
            _view.LoadUrl("https://www.google.com/");

            // 设置窗体的标题
            Text = "My Application";
        }
    }
}
```

在这个示例中，我们首先创建了一个 `Engine` 对象和一个 `WebView` 对象，并将 `Engine` 对象传递给 `WebView` 对象。

接下来，我们创建一个新的 `Panel` 控件，并将其添加到窗体中。然后，我们将 `WebView` 控件添加到 `Panel` 控件中，并使用 `DockStyle.Fill` 属性使其填充整个 `Panel` 控件。

最后，我们使用 `LoadUrl` 方法导航到指定的页面，并将窗体的标题设置为 "My Application"。

