Чтобы подключиться к бирже через WebSocket и получать данные о свечах в реальном времени, вы можете использовать следующий код:

```javascript
import React, { useEffect, useRef, useState } from 'react';
import { init, dispose, Chart } from 'klinecharts';

const CandleChart = () => {
  const chart = useRef<Chart | null>(null);
  const [socket, setSocket] = useState<WebSocket | null>(null);

  useEffect(() => {
    // Инициализация графика
    chart.current = init('chart-container-id');

    // Создание соединения с WebSocket и установка слушателя событий
    const newSocket = new WebSocket(
      'wss://fstream.binance.com/stream?streams=dogebusd@kline_1m'
    );
    newSocket.onmessage = (event) => {
      const newData = JSON.parse(event.data);
      const candleData = newData?.data?.k;
      if (candleData) {
        chart.current?.applyNewData({
          timestamp: candleData.t,
          open: parseFloat(candleData.o),
          high: parseFloat(candleData.h),
          low: parseFloat(candleData.l),
          close: parseFloat(candleData.c),
          volume: parseFloat(candleData.v),
        });
      }
    };

    setSocket(newSocket);

    // Очистка при размонтировании компонента
    return () => {
      newSocket.close();
      dispose('chart-container-id');
    };
  }, []);

  return (
    <div>
      <div id="chart-container-id" style={{ width: '100%', height: '400px' }} />
    </div>
  );
};

export default CandleChart;
```

Этот код будет подключаться к бирже Binance и обновлять график свечей для пары DOGEBUSD с интервалом 1 минута. Вы можете изменить интервал и пару, заменив аргумент `stream` в строке `wss://fstream.binance.com/stream?streams=dogebusd@kline_1m`.

是的，HttpClient确实可以自动处理cookies。为了实现这个功能，你需要使用`HttpClientHandler`并设置`UseCookies`属性为`true`。此外，你还需要使用`CookieContainer`属性来存储cookies。以下是一个使用HttpClient处理cookies的示例：

```csharp
using System;
using System.Net;
using System.Net.Http;

class Program
{
    static async Task Main(string[] args)
    {
        var cookieContainer = new CookieContainer();
        var handler = new HttpClientHandler
        {
            UseCookies = true,
            CookieContainer = cookieContainer
        };

        using var httpClient = new HttpClient(handler);

        // 发送一个带cookie的请求
        cookieContainer.Add(new Uri("https://api.example.com"), new Cookie("cookieName", "cookieValue"));
        var response = await httpClient.GetAsync("https://api.example.com/data");

        // 当服务器设置或更新cookie时，它们会自动添加到CookieContainer中
        var serverCookies = cookieContainer.GetCookies(new Uri("https://api.example.com"));

        foreach (Cookie cookie in serverCookies)
        {
            Console.WriteLine($"Cookie: {cookie.Name} = {cookie.Value}");
        }
    }
}
```

在这个示例中，我们创建一个`CookieContainer`实例来存储cookies，并在HttpClientHandler中设置`UseCookies`为`true`。这样，当HttpClient接收到带有Set-Cookie头的响应时，它将自动将这些cookies存储在`CookieContainer`中。我们还可以向`CookieContainer`中添加自定义的cookies，要发送的请求会自动包含这些cookies。

注意：创建HttpClient时，通常建议尽可能地重用HttpClient实例，以减少资源使用。你可以考虑将上面示例中的`HttpClient`和`HttpClientHandler`设置为静态变量。同时在使用完后不需要用using释放HttpClient。

可以使用其他方式来加载 USBToken 驱动并调用，例如使用 BouncyCastle 提供的 PKCS#11 Provider。

以下是 Java 代码示例：

```java
import java.io.File;
import java.io.FileInputStream;
import java.security.KeyStore;
import java.security.PrivateKey;
import java.security.Provider;
import java.security.Security;
import java.security.cert.Certificate;
import java.util.Arrays;
import java.util.Enumeration;
import java.util.Properties;

import org.bouncycastle.jce.provider.BouncyCastleProvider;
import org.bouncycastle.pkcs11.Initializer;
import org.bouncycastle.pkcs11.Slot;
import org.bouncycastle.pkcs11.TokenCodeSigner;
import org.bouncycastle.pkcs11.TokenCodeSignerBuilder;
import org.bouncycastle.pkcs11.TokenKeyStore;
import org.bouncycastle.pkcs11.config.PKCS11ProviderConfiguration;
import org.bouncycastle.pkcs11.config.ProviderConfiguration;
import org.bouncycastle.pkcs11.config.TokenConfiguration;
import org.bouncycastle.pkcs11.util.PKCS11ConnectionException;
import org.bouncycastle.util.encoders.Hex;

import com.itextpdf.text.DocumentException;
import com.itextpdf.text.Rectangle;
import com.itextpdf.text.pdf.PdfReader;
import com.itextpdf.text.pdf.PdfSignatureAppearance;
import com.itextpdf.text.pdf.PdfStamper;
import com.itextpdf.text.pdf.security.BouncyCastleDigest;
import com.itextpdf.text.pdf.security.DigestAlgorithms;
import com.itextpdf.text.pdf.security.ExternalDigest;
import com.itextpdf.text.pdf.security.ExternalSignature;
import com.itextpdf.text.pdf.security.MakeSignature.CryptoStandard;
import com.itextpdf.text.pdf.security.PrivateKeySignature;

public class USBTokenPDFSign {

    // 加载 USBToken 驱动
    static {
        try {
            // 加载 PKCS#11 Provider
            Properties pkcs11Config = new Properties();
            pkcs11Config.setProperty("PKCS11_NATIVE_MODULE", "eps2003csp11.dll");
            pkcs11Config.setProperty("SLOT_ID", "1");
            pkcs11Config.setProperty("TOKEN_LABEL", "USBToken");
            ProviderConfiguration pkcs11ProviderConfig = new PKCS11ProviderConfiguration(pkcs11Config);
            Provider pkcs11Provider = new BouncyCastleProvider();
            Security.addProvider(pkcs11Provider);
            Initializer.initialize(pkcs11ProviderConfig, pkcs11Provider);

            // 初始化 TokenKeyStore
            TokenConfiguration tokenConfig = TokenConfiguration.newBuilder().setSlotId(1).setTokenLabel("USBToken")
                    .build();
            Provider pkcs11ProviderWithToken = Security.getProvider("BCPKCS11-" + tokenConfig.getSlotId());
            TokenCodeSigner tokenCodeSigner = new TokenCodeSignerBuilder(pkcs11ProviderWithToken)
                    .withToken(tokenConfig).build();
            TokenKeyStore tokenKeyStore = TokenKeyStore.Builder.newBuilder()
                    .withConfiguration(new PKCS11ProviderConfiguration(pkcs11Config)).withToken(tokenConfig)
                    .withCodeSigner(tokenCodeSigner).build();
        } catch (Exception e) {
            e.printStackTrace();
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {
        // 在 USBToken 中存储私钥和证书
        String usbTokenPin = "123456";
        char[] keyStorePassword = usbTokenPin.toCharArray();
        String keyStoreType = "PKCS11";
        String certAlias = "test_cert";

        // PDF 文件路径
        String pdfFilePath = "D:\\test.pdf";
        // 签名后 PDF 文件路径
        String signedPdfFilePath = "D:\\test_signed.pdf";

        // 获取并打印 USBToken 中的证书信息
        KeyStore keyStore = KeyStore.getInstance(keyStoreType);
        keyStore.load(null, keyStorePassword);
        KeyStore.Builder builder = KeyStore.Builder.newInstance(keyStoreType, null, null, new KeyStore.CallbackHandlerProtection(new KeyStore.CallbackHandlerProtection.AuthCallbackHandler(usbTokenPin.toCharArray())));
        keyStore = builder.getKeyStore();
        Enumeration<String> aliasesEnum = keyStore.aliases();
        while (aliasesEnum.hasMoreElements()) {
            String alias = aliasesEnum.nextElement();
            Certificate cert = keyStore.getCertificate(alias);
            System.out.println("USBToken alias: " + alias);
            System.out.println("- Certificate Fingerprint: "
                    + Hex.toHexString(cert.getEncoded()));
        }
        Certificate cert = keyStore.getCertificate(certAlias);
        PrivateKey privateKey = (PrivateKey) keyStore.getKey(certAlias, null);

        // 加载 PDF 文件并进行数字签名
        File pdfFile = new File(pdfFilePath);
        PdfReader pdfReader = new PdfReader(new FileInputStream(pdfFile));
        PdfStamper pdfStamper = PdfStamper.createSignature(pdfReader, new FileOutputStream(signedPdfFilePath), '\0');
        PdfSignatureAppearance signatureAppearance = pdfStamper.getSignatureAppearance();
        signatureAppearance.setReason("Digitally signed PDF document");
        signatureAppearance.setLocation("Shanghai");
        signatureAppearance.setContact("contact@example.com");
        signatureAppearance.setSignatureGraphic(new FileInputStream("signature.jpg"));
        signatureAppearance.setCertificationLevel(PdfSignatureAppearance.CERTIFIED_NO_CHANGES_ALLOWED);
        signatureAppearance.setVisibleSignature(new Rectangle(36, 36, 144, 144), 1, null);
        ExternalDigest externalDigest = new BouncyCastleDigest();
        ExternalSignature externalSignature = new PrivateKeySignature(privateKey, DigestAlgorithms.SHA256, null);
        pdfStamper.setSignaturePolicy("2.16.840.1.101.3.2.1.48.1");
        pdfStamper.setCertificationLevel(0);
        pdfStamper.setSignatureEvent(new USBTokenSignatureEvent(externalDigest, externalSignature, null, certAlias));
        pdfStamper.close();
        pdfReader.close();
    }

    // 自定义签名事件处理器，用于调用 USBToken 进行数字签名
    public static class USBTokenSignatureEvent implements PdfStamper.SignatureEvent {
        private ExternalDigest digest;
        private ExternalSignature signature;
        private Certificate[] chain;
        private String certAlias;

        public USBTokenSignatureEvent(ExternalDigest digest, ExternalSignature signature, Certificate[] chain,
                String certAlias) {
            this.digest = digest;
            this.signature = signature;
            this.chain = chain;
            this.certAlias = certAlias;
        }

        @Override
        public void getSignatureDictionary(PdfDictionary sig) {
        }

        @Override
        public void modifySigningDictionary(PdfDictionary signDic) {
        }

        @Override
        public byte[] sign(InputStream data) throws SignatureException {
            try {
                byte[] messageDigest = digest.getMessageDigest().digest(IOUtils.toByteArray(data));
                PrivateKey privateKey = signature.getPrivateKey();
                java.security.Signature jcaSignature = java.security.Signature.getInstance(signature.getAlgorithm());
                jcaSignature.initSign(privateKey);
                jcaSignature.update(messageDigest);
                return jcaSignature.sign();
            } catch (Exception e) {
                throw new SignatureException(e);
            }
        }

        @Override
        public void modifySignatureDictionary(PdfDictionary signDic) {
            signDic.put(PdfName.NAME, new PdfString(certAlias));
        }

        @Override
        public Certificate[] getChain() {
            return chain;
        }

        @Override
        public void setSignDate(Calendar signDate) {
        }
    }
}
``` 

注意：在使用 BouncyCastle 使用 PKCS#11 Provider 时，需要引入 bcpkix-jdk15on 和 bcprov-jdk15on 的相关依赖。

